OL,3,CFilm festival takes place to celebrate
OL,4,C50 years of Portuguese democracy
OL,6,FPeople in have been learning about
OL,7,FPortugal's 1974 revolution through a
OL,8,Fspecial film festival.
OL,10,FTo celebrate 50 years since the
OL,11,Fcountry became a democracy, the 13th
OL,12,FParish International Film Festival has
OL,13,Fpartnered with Agencia, the Portuguese
OL,14,FShort Film Agency.
OL,16,FThe movies represented the times
OL,17,Fbefore, during and after the Carnation
OL,18,FRevolution - with themes looking at
OL,19,Fresistance and fascism, and the
OL,20,Fmemories and trauma of the war.
