OL,3,CFilm festival takes place to celebrate
OL,4,C50 years of Portuguese democracy
OL,6,FThe festival's co-ordinator Una
OL,7,FLanglois said: "It's always our aim in
OL,8,Fthe 13th Parish Festival to have a
OL,9,Fdiverse and accessible programme,
OL,10,Freaching out to as many islanders,
OL,11,Ftastes, genres and interests as
OL,12,Fpossible.
OL,14,F"We're hoping that this will continue
OL,15,Fto grow in future - our festival is
OL,16,Falways a celebration of incredible
OL,17,Ffilms and stories, told in many
OL,18,Fformats and in many languages. A
OL,19,Fcelebration of people, places and
OL,20,Fthings!"
