OL,3,CFilm festival takes place to celebrate
OL,4,C50 years of Portuguese democracy
OL,6,FThe festival's programme included a
OL,7,Fbrief overview of how the Estado Novo,
OL,8,Fthe Colonial War and the Revolution of
OL,9,F25 April 1974 were portrayed through
OL,10,FPortuguese cinema.
OL,12,FThe Director of Jersey's Film
OL,13,FFestival, Tony Langlois, said it is
OL,14,F"an important story for the Portuguese
OL,15,Fobviously because it was their road to
OL,16,Fdemocracy."
OL,18,FHe added: "We want to recognise the
OL,19,Fcultural diversity of the island in
OL,20,Fthe work that we do.
